{"tid":1504317,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"荃灣區示威者暴力升級","createTime":"2019-08-25T09:50:48.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-25T09:59:16.000Z","uid":212626,"like":1,"dislike":15,"uniUserReply":16,"replies":[{"pid":"1f97b15672ebcff9655c18315cb8221e9dee0122","tid":1504317,"uid":212626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-25T09:50:48.000Z","msg":"荃灣區示威者暴力升級<br />\n＊＊＊＊＊＊＊＊＊＊＊<br />\n電台及電視台當值宣布員注意：<br />\n <br />\n請盡快播出下列消息，並在適當時間重播：<br />\n <br />\n  激進示威者繼續在荃灣區堵塞多條道路，包括聯仁街、楊屋道和德士古道，導致現場一帶交通十分擠塞。<br />\n   <br />\n  期間示威者的暴力程度升級，除設置路障外，亦向警務人員投擲雜物及用鐳射光線照射警務人員。此外，示威者也於路邊挖掘磚頭，有機會危害在場人士和警務人員的人身安全。<br />\n   <br />\n  警方再次重申，將於短時間內使用<span style=\"color: red;\">最低的相應武力</span>驅散，現呼籲在場人士立即離開。警方對示威者一切暴力行為，予以譴責。<br />\n  <br />\n <br />\n完<br />\n2019年8月25日（星期日）<br />\n香港時間17時36分<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.info.gov.hk/gia/general/201908/25/P2019082500776.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.info.gov.hk%2Fgia%2Fgeneral%2F201908%2F25%2FP2019082500776.htm&d=6v%2BmLhPCoO19KIzpXGl1DiMX%2BuEjOoKUanh%2Bi4Xf2cM%3D&h=d3fb53bb\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.info.gov.hk/gia/general/201908/25/P2019082500776.htm</a>"},{"pid":"e919368a0d6b0877e22b3e50582f14aba9c4ac3c","tid":1504317,"uid":272119,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-25T09:51:08.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/photo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d2924fed6397f0601616f46fd129a0d6b6dfe29b","tid":1504317,"uid":141070,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-25T09:51:20.000Z","msg":"快開槍<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f50debd5877e42749ba0cca91c04aca4fa3040ca","tid":1504317,"uid":247845,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-25T09:51:26.000Z","msg":"離開你老母 點離開呀仆街"},{"pid":"90c442be552c0b8744b60bfe9b57638b8def0c51","tid":1504317,"uid":55130,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-25T09:51:42.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/p